# Path configuration for AI Docker Sandbox
#
# This file serves as a template for local configuration.
# Copy it to the project root as .env and replace the values
# with your local absolute paths.
#
# IMPORTANT: The .env file is ignored by Git for security reasons.
# NEVER commit the .env file with your personal paths.

# Absolute path to the ai-docker project root directory
# Example on macOS/Linux: /Users/your_username/Documents/Projects/ai-docker
# Example on Windows: C:\Users\your_username\Documents\Projects\ai-docker
AI_DOCKER_BASE=/Users/your_username/Documents/Projects/ai-docker

# Absolute path to the directory containing your secrets and API keys
# This folder should contain .env files with your sensitive API keys
# In the secrets/ai-docker folder you will have a .env file with your keys: GITHUB_TOKEN=xxx, CONTEXT7_TOKEN=xxx, etc.
# Example: /Users/your_username/Documents/Secrets/ai-docker
AI_SECRETS_BASE=/Users/your_username/Documents/Secrets/ai-docker
